author: Adam Savage’s Tested
description:
Adam unwraps a selection of beautiful felted wool characters created by the talented Felted Friends! The needle felted skill on display in these pieces of art is impressive, and Adam could not be more delighted by the personality that shines through in each!

Find Felted Friends' creations at: https://www.feltedfriends.shop/ and https://www.facebook.com/feltedfriends.19

Shot by Josh Self 
Music by Jinglepunks
